{"word":"στολίζω","slug":"στολίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>στολίζω</b></el> <el>(στολίζω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:στολίς'><el>στολίς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to put in trim</i>, <el>στολίσας νηὸς πτερά</el> <i>having trimmed</i> the sails, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to equip, dress</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ἐστολισμένος δορί</el> <i>armed</i> with spear, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>to deck, adorn</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}